.SYNOPSIS...
Issued at 344 AM PDT Wed Jun 28 2023

A gradual warming trend will continue through midweek with hot
temperatures across the interior by Friday and throughout the
holiday weekend. Meanwhile, cooler conditions will prevail near
the coast/bays in response to onshore winds. Temperatures moderate
back to near normal early next week and into the 4th of July
Holiday.

